      "resolution_level": 4,
      "anchor_concept_id": "spine_mathematics_l3_line_integrals",
      "content": {
        "title": "Vector Line Integrals",
        "definition": "Work integral ∫_C F · dr = ∫_C P dx + Q dy + R dz computing work done by force field F along path C.",
        "summary": "Vector line integrals measure circulation and work and depend on path unless the field is conservative."
      },
